headline: KEYCORP LOWERS ITS PRIME LENDING RATE TO 7.50 PERCENT
summary: KeyCorp (NYSE: KEY) and its banking affiliates have lowered their prime lending rate to 7.50 percent from 7.75 percent, effective tomorrow, Dec. 19, 2024.
